Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.22,0:01:32.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  這邊不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.95,0:01:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.65,0:01:34.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紙燈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.77,0:01:35.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就幫你拿來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.87,0:01:36.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.99,0:01:44.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緒花  你那邊忙好了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.08,0:01:45.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.53,0:01:51.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過難得來那麼多客人  真是可惜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.82,0:01:55.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  在許願板上要寫什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.42,0:01:58.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？ 我還沒決定好…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.14,0:02:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  好好想一想啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.65,0:02:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似還很靈驗的哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.41,0:02:04.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢想啊野心什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.47,0:02:06.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢想…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.81,0:02:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結名我呀～總而言之就是好想留學～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.14,0:02:14.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想在外國學一些關於旅館的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.20,0:02:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有還有～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.79,0:02:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一位嬌小的女性神明
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.78,0:02:22.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了報答用紙燈照亮她的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.89,0:02:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而把他們的願望帶到天上去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.41,0:02:32.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來到湯乃鷺後  我希望自己能夠閃耀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.55,0:02:37.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後每天都過得手忙腳亂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.58,0:02:41.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我覺得自己已經喜歡上工作和喜翠莊了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.02,0:02:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我的夢想是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.28,0:02:45.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.46,0:02:47.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.77,0:02:48.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了緒花
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.66,0:02:51.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.02,0:02:58.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人數如此眾多
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.27,0:02:59.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考慮到晚餐的籌備
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.10,0:03:03.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能夠盡可能地削減花在早餐上的勞力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.73,0:03:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.03,0:03:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早餐不要送到客房  而是用自助餐的形式
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.10,0:03:09.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.05,0:03:10.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.11,0:03:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我想會有客人喜歡在房間裡慢慢吃早飯的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.66,0:03:18.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也沒法子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.16,0:03:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廚房已經忙不過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.63,0:03:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,民子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.25,0:03:25.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人退房後打掃房間也很難辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.12,0:03:27.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜子她們還要去上學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.61,0:03:29.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再使用每個房間都由專人負責的形式了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.63,0:03:30.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也會幫忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.63,0:03:32.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們還在攬客嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.22,0:03:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老闆娘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.74,0:03:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吩咐過你們不要再接待客人了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.13,0:03:41.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是其他旅館攬得更多都沒事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.78,0:03:44.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看你們這麼多人不停叫喚著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.83,0:03:46.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還叫沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.26,0:03:50.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不是要降低服務的品質
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.17,0:03:53.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是要努力下一番工夫來克服眼前的困境
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.19,0:03:56.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是自助餐  料理還是料理
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.45,0:03:58.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們絕沒有半點想偷工減料的打算
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.17,0:04:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服務也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.80,0:04:01.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管沒有專門負責的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.97,0:04:03.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在其他所有方面上  我都…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.18,0:04:11.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  隨你們喜歡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.66,0:04:12.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老闆娘…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.53,0:04:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過相對地
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.14,0:04:19.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有雪洞祭  你們得用以往的方式給我好好幹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.17,0:04:24.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不能輸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.78,0:04:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.13,0:04:35.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.74,0:04:39.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個…這些是許願板
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.98,0:04:43.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38}再說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.92,0:04:44.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38}不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.20,0:04:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…在上面寫上各自的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.40,0:04:47.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掛在紙燈上…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.48,0:04:48.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.69,0:04:49.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  緒花
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.27,0:04:51.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不是做那些的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.73,0:04:55.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.69,0:05:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我拿一塊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.84,0:05:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總感覺有點不對
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.23,0:05:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一樣希望喜翠莊可以繼續開下去但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.04,0:05:18.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小民…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.55,0:05:20.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你罷手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.72,0:05:21.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.60,0:05:24.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再站在老闆娘那一邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.94,0:05:26.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是站哪一邊什麼的啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.51,0:05:27.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你倒好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.91,0:05:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有能回的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.98,0:05:31.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能回的…地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.69,0:05:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我就沒有！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.20,0:05:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有這裡！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.37,0:05:38.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟雪洞祭什麼的根本沒有關係！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.95,0:05:42.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡有…我的夢想在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.84,0:05:47.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本以為…本以為你跟我一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.21,0:05:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還高興過那麼一陣…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.56,0:05:52.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小民！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.97,0:05:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.78,0:06:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在喜翠莊工作的所有人都是好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.66,0:06:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小菜… 怎麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.82,0:06:30.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要在這裡住上一陣  沒關係吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.12,0:06:31.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是無所謂啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.07,0:06:33.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但睡那地方沒問題嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.23,0:06:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白天實在是忙不過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.99,0:06:36.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想多出一點力…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.74,0:06:39.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在努力嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.87,0:06:45.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在努力…大家雖然都在努力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.66,0:06:47.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我不覺得大家有在雪願
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.35,0:06:48.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.32,0:06:51.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.38,0:06:54.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  與其要睡那邊的話  不如到我床上…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.33,0:06:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜子  快點睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.98,0:06:58.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天四點就要起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.06,0:06:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38}小民
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.46,0:06:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四…四點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.90,0:07:01.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但現在都已經過了十二點了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.39,0:07:14.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得小菜也在這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.41,0:07:17.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻連聊天都不能聊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.18,0:07:19.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在是太沉悶了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.36,0:07:25.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣子…實在有點…討厭…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.72,0:07:37.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.76,0:07:43.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可沒工夫悠悠哉哉地散步哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.38,0:07:45.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也要幫忙的是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.56,0:07:49.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會幫你在大家面前說句話的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.95,0:07:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你站在老闆娘那邊也只會被大家孤立
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.69,0:07:53.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.64,0:07:56.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是站哪一邊的問題…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.52,0:07:57.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.84,0:08:00.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不想讓喜翠莊重振旗鼓嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.28,0:08:01.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  我都說了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.53,0:08:04.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你不是平時的你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.61,0:08:07.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是平時的你的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.36,0:08:10.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用別人說  早就自顧自地把事情攪得一團糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.65,0:08:12.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後硬是帶來一種樂觀向上的氣氛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.27,0:08:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒這回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.15,0:08:15.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而那樣的你卻…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.83,0:08:20.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變的不是喜翠莊  而是你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.28,0:08:32.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先在大廳裡接待客人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.68,0:08:33.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認他們的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.10,0:08:35.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更不要忘了問早安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.93,0:08:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.89,0:08:37.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.47,0:08:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.68,0:08:40.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.84,0:08:42.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.68,0:08:43.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.05,0:08:49.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜子  要添粥了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.87,0:08:50.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.37,0:08:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害  這個煮菜相當講究呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.51,0:08:57.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到自助餐裡都能吃到那麼棒的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.38,0:08:59.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不是～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.61,0:09:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用符合時節的食材
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.74,0:09:03.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,配合上獨到的精湛手藝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.08,0:09:05.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家也都說好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.83,0:09:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.37,0:09:09.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.57,0:09:14.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早餐全都變成自助式的了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.39,0:09:16.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是的  就是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.92,0:09:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.09,0:09:22.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是以前那種悠閒的氣氛更好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.83,0:09:24.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行啦  這樣也挺開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.89,0:09:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  果然還是間隔大些比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.11,0:09:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.46,0:09:32.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是再往左邊點好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.74,0:09:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.39,0:09:38.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊  我打算用當地畫家的作品把這裡佈置成畫廊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.14,0:09:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也可以帶來一筆可觀的收入
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.38,0:09:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會變的  喜翠莊會變的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.60,0:09:48.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緒花你也…咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.08,0:09:52.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜翠莊會變…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.18,0:09:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是變了  我最喜歡的喜翠莊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.72,0:09:58.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有雪洞祭…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.88,0:10:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還想讓阿孝看看的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.19,0:10:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  想讓朋友看看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.48,0:10:08.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.23,0:10:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不再接待客人了對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.17,0:10:13.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這間房可以的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.35,0:10:16.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.80,0:10:18.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想讓他看看喜翠莊是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.06,0:10:22.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣  讓他作為你的朋友留宿在這裡便好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.75,0:10:25.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老  老闆娘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.63,0:10:28.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你身體啊情緒啊什麼的還好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.24,0:10:29.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.01,0:10:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為老闆娘怎麼會那麼好心…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.08,0:10:39.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是你重要的朋友對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.85,0:10:41.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.29,0:10:43.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在是非常感謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.27,0:10:50.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鶴來  喂——  民子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.68,0:10:52.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  徹先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.92,0:10:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到民子公主的睡相了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.12,0:10:55.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38}喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.51,0:10:57.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個徹是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.13,0:11:08.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…吶  小民
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.14,0:11:08.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38}別來跟我說話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.18,0:11:13.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是在跟你賭氣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.16,0:11:14.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.06,0:11:17.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為緒花你站在老闆娘那一邊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.70,0:11:21.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鶴來同學她喜歡緒花的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.91,0:11:28.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是不那麼想…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.49,0:11:30.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,湯底熬得怎樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.77,0:11:31.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就去看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.05,0:11:33.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,民子  把蔬菜給洗了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.65,0:11:34.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.98,0:11:37.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些結束之後就去處理鴨子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.24,0:11:38.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.87,0:11:41.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管在什麼地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.46,0:11:43.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都如徹先生所說  能做一位廚師
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.95,0:11:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…  我之所以執著於這裡的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.60,0:11:51.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為有徹先生在  有蓮先生在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.61,0:11:54.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有大家在…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.53,0:11:57.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.66,0:11:59.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種奇怪的東西怎麼能拿得出手！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.19,0:12:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.76,0:12:01.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38}我說  蓮先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.96,0:12:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.87,0:12:03.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.87,0:12:05.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小碗配菜怎麼還沒準備好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.37,0:12:07.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人已經開始抱怨了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.33,0:12:12.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然要換掉配菜 麻煩的可是我這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.77,0:12:14.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 蓮先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.04,0:12:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}你居然把錯推到我頭上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.57,0:12:17.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼怎麼  兩位到底怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.61,0:12:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}你來廚房抱怨之前  就不能想想自己能幹些什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.27,0:12:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不是爭吵的時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.18,0:12:21.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}你說什麼！別把廚房的問題推給我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.25,0:12:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此刻必須齊心合力…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.70,0:12:22.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}看你像塊豆腐一樣禁不住事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.90,0:12:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}你懂什麼這叫敏感
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.56,0:12:25.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純潔的心靈才是最珍貴的你不懂嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.62,0:12:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.57,0:12:29.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是要保護喜翠莊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.14,0:12:33.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜翠莊…現在是重要關頭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.25,0:12:35.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再吵架了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.58,0:12:38.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.76,0:12:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請走好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.93,0:12:48.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.17,0:12:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  告個別
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.44,0:12:51.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.43,0:12:55.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得有點不對勁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.02,0:13:00.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡喜翠莊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.19,0:13:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為這是個能讓客人高興的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.38,0:13:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是大家一起努力  連我也一起感覺到很幸福的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.72,0:13:12.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  現在喜翠莊卻不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.84,0:13:15.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都只在意老闆娘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.04,0:13:18.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  緒花
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.82,0:13:21.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是已經知道老闆娘真正的心意了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.88,0:13:24.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.11,0:13:26.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.67,0:13:31.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我最喜歡的喜翠莊  是老闆娘一手創造的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.58,0:13:33.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小菜…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.37,0:13:40.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想勉強別人去附和她的夢想嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.50,0:13:44.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老闆娘是不會明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.50,0:13:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為她自己是能夠奔跑的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.25,0:13:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然沒有自己的夢想  不能奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.89,0:13:55.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是只要能夠去追隨那些有著夢想的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.71,0:13:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這便是他們的夢想了  這樣的人也是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.65,0:14:16.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天就要正式開始了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.16,0:14:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.26,0:14:20.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決定許願板上要寫什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.54,0:14:21.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.40,0:14:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那喜翠莊的人的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.80,0:14:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給他們了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.11,0:14:29.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…因為一直手忙腳亂的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.84,0:14:33.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒～我說  緒花你是不是被無視了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.81,0:14:35.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會  不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.88,0:14:36.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38}明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.58,0:14:39.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結名我去幫你催催
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.74,0:14:41.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 結名同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.51,0:14:42.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38}不等你～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.37,0:14:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38}我說結名同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.02,0:14:45.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.66,0:14:50.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.74,0:14:56.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就快到祭典了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.17,0:14:59.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遊客們從各地趕來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.87,0:15:03.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人是從東京來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.67,0:15:04.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.99,0:15:07.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…因為打扮的這麼豔麗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.56,0:15:09.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看得出嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.35,0:15:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.10,0:15:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豆丁老爺  好痛  好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.17,0:15:14.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38}怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.05,0:15:16.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扭到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.89,0:15:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦啊  在這重要關頭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.35,0:15:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去向協會求救吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.46,0:15:22.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.26,0:15:24.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們家也去問過了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.04,0:15:26.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是雪洞祭前夕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.58,0:15:27.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒有人手了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.82,0:15:28.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.43,0:15:34.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪洞祭前早餐和服務都要按以往的方式去做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.68,0:15:36.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是和老闆娘約好的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.46,0:15:37.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.06,0:15:39.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去和老闆娘認錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.22,0:15:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換個做法的話一定還有辦法…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.97,0:15:44.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要繼續幹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.08,0:15:46.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  給我老實待著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.44,0:15:47.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還怎麼能老實待著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.35,0:15:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.27,0:15:51.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就輸給老闆娘了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.83,0:15:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輸給…老闆娘嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.90,0:15:58.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作要分輸贏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.56,0:15:59.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.55,0:16:00.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣太奇怪了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.15,0:16:05.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起讓客人開心  贏過老闆娘更重要嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.56,0:16:07.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不贏的話喜翠莊就沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.97,0:16:08.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.72,0:16:09.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.55,0:16:10.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要再吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.36,0:16:13.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜子…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.87,0:16:16.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡喜翠莊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.05,0:16:17.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜歡了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.52,0:16:21.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是現在的喜翠莊不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.61,0:16:24.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我喜歡的喜翠莊還給我！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.65,0:16:25.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還給我！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.32,0:16:30.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易才找到能釋放自我的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.22,0:16:37.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡喜翠莊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.56,0:16:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在場的各位都是同一個心情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.72,0:16:44.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是同一個心情  卻又不知為何背道而馳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.92,0:16:47.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜翠莊已經是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.00,0:16:51.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  虛幻之城
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.13,0:16:54.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.67,0:16:58.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是說一下大家的心聲…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.32,0:17:01.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來代替吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.51,0:17:03.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老闆娘
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.04,0:17:06.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來做女服務員的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.44,0:17:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就能彌補巴的缺口了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.89,0:17:10.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.50,0:17:16.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.75,0:17:19.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.48,0:17:20.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.46,0:17:21.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換換心情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.79,0:17:23.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三天兩夜  大人一位
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.10,0:17:26.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐現在預約已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.32,0:17:27.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不是說這個的時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.62,0:17:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事  和緒花一個房間好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.72,0:17:33.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我住的話  工作我也能幫幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.07,0:17:37.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在這裡那麼大聲的爭吵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.40,0:17:40.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明這麼忙前台卻一個人都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.84,0:17:42.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽  真的要幫忙…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.42,0:17:43.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.38,0:17:46.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緣…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.41,0:17:48.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這場戰鬥是我們的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.26,0:17:52.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓老闆娘…還讓姐姐來幫忙的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.97,0:17:56.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.09,0:17:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要抱有個人感情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.41,0:18:01.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是要保護喜翠莊嗎  Anything
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.33,0:18:03.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崇子…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.48,0:18:07.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Anything…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.57,0:18:23.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是  到了雪洞祭當天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.14,0:18:37.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.37,0:18:46.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  這就過去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.30,0:18:50.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崇子  現在就去月之間…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.57,0:18:51.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  忙不過來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.91,0:18:54.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓姐姐去？但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.12,0:18:57.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少爺  月之間是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.02,0:18:58.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.67,0:19:04.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浴衣的尺寸  把M換成L
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.05,0:19:04.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.45,0:19:07.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.30,0:19:11.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少爺  今天我是女服務員
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.28,0:19:14.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要好好發出指示
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.25,0:19:17.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老闆娘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.05,0:19:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稱呼錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.15,0:19:20.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不該是老闆娘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.06,0:19:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 請多關照了  翠女士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.12,0:19:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,民子  漬菜拼盤呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.50,0:19:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就剩下裝飾了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.89,0:19:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燒烤好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.48,0:19:33.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.80,0:19:35.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來是波之間 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.26,0:19:36.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.86,0:19:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜子  這邊交給我好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.02,0:19:40.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.21,0:19:43.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這腳打掃還是沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.47,0:19:44.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宴會場那邊拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.13,0:19:45.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.13,0:19:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.77,0:19:54.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 停
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.65,0:19:56.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.86,0:19:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來是鶴之間  鶴之間…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.69,0:20:02.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老闆娘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.22,0:20:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老闆娘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.80,0:20:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.52,0:20:07.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是有點搖搖晃晃而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.24,0:20:09.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是休息一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.97,0:20:14.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅館生意客人最重要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.94,0:20:17.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己只能排第二第三
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.77,0:20:22.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是呀  我卻對此樂在其中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.74,0:20:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老闆娘…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.15,0:20:26.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  回到你的工作崗位上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.22,0:20:28.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.28,0:20:36.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.92,0:20:37.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雕刻就交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.24,0:20:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.73,0:20:41.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤之間還沒好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.28,0:20:42.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.12,0:20:42.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.20,0:20:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓮先生  天婦羅炸好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.41,0:20:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤之間的我拿走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.81,0:20:48.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.93,0:20:51.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家在這裡努力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.31,0:20:52.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}慢死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.08,0:20:53.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.89,0:20:57.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽和老闆娘一起工作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.24,0:20:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}一路走好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.36,0:20:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}明白了  壽之間是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.49,0:21:00.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.30,0:21:03.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.01,0:21:35.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.20,0:21:41.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好累
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.54,0:21:44.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都用完餐了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.08,0:21:47.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.82,0:21:50.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了大家  我們渡過了難關
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.67,0:21:51.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.54,0:21:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算告一段落了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.90,0:21:56.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒時間鬆懈了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.55,0:21:57.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家該出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.11,0:21:58.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出發？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.65,0:22:01.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是去參加雪洞祭
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.19,0:23:33.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡你  最喜歡了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.75,0:23:37.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}如果能被原諒的話  希望能再一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.73,0:23:37.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}我終於找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.12,0:23:40.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的…

